## Best Practices
1. Always test responsive behavior
2. Maintain accessibility (aria-labels, semantic HTML)
3. Optimize images using Next.js Image component when possible
4. Use state management appropriately (useState, useEffect)
5. Handle loading and error states
6. Keep bundle size in mind when adding dependencies

